title: Does Canberra need a road diet? ACT Greens MLA Shane Rattenbury thinks so
text:
Does Canberra need a road diet? ACT G... Does Canberra need a road diet? ACT Greens MLA Shane Rattenbury thinks so Next Story Prev Story 58 min ago Read more: The Age 
Shane Rattenbury says if we overindulge in road building, Canberra will become a car-centric city that is congested and polluted. Immediate temptations are always there.   The Age.
